Title: Creating a Single View from Legacy Systems

Span.Text: Connect disparate IT systems and agency management systems, such as stores and supplies, fleet management, prisoner transportation, prison operations, and CCTV security to help improve operational effectiveness and efficiency. Microsoft technology and partner solutions bring the information together, creating an interoperable solution that can be monitored from a command and control centre in virtually any location, with alert notifications delivered through multiple devices via user defined escalation rules.
